{"tid":1385614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(鍵盤戰士召集) 蔣元秋放流料屈義士","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T23:53:37.000Z","uid":287583,"like":105,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cae690761584d911a6c4a634732045c1984825","tid":1385614,"uid":287583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<br />\n<br />\n義士係沙田被拉，之後提堂<br />\n事後藍絲用假fb AC扮義士懺悔，大造文章<br />\n朋友識義士本人<br />\n已經問左義士本人fact checked<br />\n個AC係假嘅<br />\n所以蔣元秋係專登放流料 做假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DOZ717t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDOZ717t.png&h=d8adb737&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QA2YpkZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQA2YpkZ.png&h=e544e0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們，已經有好多義士犧牲左。<br />\n事後仲要飽受克警、法庭、外界攻擊<br />\n依家仲要比藍絲誣捏<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要事後保護佢地，以免佢地覺得係用完即棄嘅犧牲品<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/537711586254667/posts/3526807910678338?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F537711586254667%2Fposts%2F3526807910678338%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=4bf901b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/537711586254667/posts/3526807910678338?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫手report個post同澄清下🙏🙏<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n有啲市民都因為保護連儂牆或者幫義士都俾藍絲起底圍插<br />\n我地更加要保護佢地<br />\n香港人齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"125ad8fcd0f0267d3c7ba412c884bb7fb85d75c0","tid":1385614,"uid":61979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01978f3a8715aa957cba8a52ee04042a8d0ee822","tid":1385614,"uid":166616,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"睇元秋fb 留言啲五毛 就知咩人支持咩人"},{"p